1.9
log
@unifdef CPU_XSCALE_PXA2X0, ARM_MMU_XSCALE, ARM_MMU_GENERIC (armv3)
and remove some xscale definitions.

ok kettenis@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: pte.h,v 1.8 2016/08/27 14:22:35 kettenis Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: pte.h,v 1.6 2003/04/18 11:08:28 scw Exp $	*/

/*
